# matrix
# introduction
%%visits: 2
Matrices were first developed to solved a system of linear equations, which are things like $$
2x + 2y = 20
5x +  y = 42
$$
So when thinking about any other property, it is helpful to always remember that a matrix at it's core has rules that make it so that it is sensible to use in a system of linear equations, specifically [[linear_diophantine_equation]]s
